title: My launcher is not working
body: i tried to get on earlier it will pop up the league of legends then it doesn't open at all and it is not showing in my task manager. so i uninstalled and reinstalled through this site and still having the same situation.

replies.body: This issue is usually caused by a setting or program blocking the patcher from launching.  Go over the steps in the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to restore access.  Let me know if you have any questions.
